Chairman of Ovia South-West Local Government Council, Destiny Enabulele, has presented the 2018 budget estimates of N3.286.291.144.50 billion to the legislative arm of the council for approval. The budget christened, “Budget of Total Transformation,” has the sum of N1,900,264,317,12 billion, representing 57.8 percent for recurrent expenditure, and N1.386,026,827,38 billion, representing 42.2 percent for capital expenditure….